                    <p>
                      CitySafe is a web-based disaster response app that provides
                      real-time alerts, localized notifications, and reliable information
                      during emergencies. It helps citizens stay informed, empowers them
                      to send SOS requests for immediate assistance, and supports city officials and
                      responders in coordinating relief efforts efficiently.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                      CitySafe was developed as a <span>Capstone
                        Research Project</span> entitled “CitySafe: Urban Disaster Response App”, with the goal of
                      creating a user-friendly, efficient, and compassionate system that strengthens disaster resilience
                      in urban areas.
